  "hashtags": ["#MakeInIndia", "#IndiaManufacturing", "#ElectronicsManufacturing", "#PCBManufacturing", "#CuCircuits", "#HardwareStartup", "#AtmanirbharBharat"],
  "caption": "\"The day is not far when India will be the hub of industrial manufacturing and the world will be looking towards it.\"\n\nPM Narendra Modi said this. And the numbers are proving him right.\n\n99% of mobile phones sold in India are now manufactured domestically. Mobile imports dropped 85%. Manufacturing jobs surged 200% between 2022 and 2024. India is targeting $300 billion in electronics production.\n\nThis is not distant future talk. This is happening now.\n\nAt Cu Circuits, we are proud to be part of this story. Every PCB we fabricate in Chennai is one more component that does not need to be imported. Every 3D printed prototype we deliver helps an Indian hardware startup move faster.\n\nThe manufacturing revolution is not coming. It is here.\n\nWhat are you building? We would love to fabricate it.\n\n#MakeInIndia #IndiaManufacturing #ElectronicsManufacturing #PCBManufacturing #CuCircuits #HardwareStartup #AtmanirbharBharat",
  "strategy": {"format": "quote_data_mashup", "visual_approach": "large inspirational quote with attribution at top, data visualization below"},
  "html": "<div style=\"width:1080px; height:1350px; background:#0D0D0D; position:relative; overflow:hidden; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;\">\n\n  <!-- Background texture: diagonal lines -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 60px, rgba(184,115,51,0.02) 60px, rgba(184,115,51,0.02) 61px); \"></div>\n\n  <!-- Top accent bar -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:5px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, #B87333, #E8A04C, #2E8B57);\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Cu Logo -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:36px; left:40px; width:64px; height:64px; background:#B87333; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:28px; font-weight:800; color:#0D0D0D; letter-spacing:1px;\">Cu</div>\n\n  <!-- Tag -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:44px; left:130px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:#E8A04C; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:3px; text-transform:uppercase;\">VISION + DATA</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Quote Section -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:130px; left:40px; right:40px;\">\n    <!-- Large quotation mark -->\n    <div style=\"font-size:120px; color:rgba(184,115,51,0.25); font-family:Georgia,serif; line-height:0.6; margin-bottom:10px;\">&#8220;</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF; line-height:1.35; margin-top:-20px; padding-left:10px; padding-right:20px;\">The day is not far when India will be the hub of industrial manufacturing and the world will be looking towards it.</div>\n    <!-- Attribution -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:14px; margin-top:24px; padding-left:10px;\">\n      <div style=\"width:4px; height:40px; background:#B87333; border-radius:2px;\"></div>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:#B87333;\">Narendra Modi</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);\">Prime Minister of India</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Divider -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:520px; left:40px; right:40px; height:1px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(184,115,51,0.3), transparent);\"></div>\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:510px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); background:#0D0D0D; padding:0 20px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:#B87333; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:3px;\">THE NUMBERS BACK IT UP</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Data Cards Row 1 -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:560px; left:40px; right:40px; display:flex; gap:20px;\">\n\n    <!-- Big stat: 99% -->\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(46,139,87,0.15) 0%, rgba(46,139,87,0.05) 100%); border:1px solid rgba(46,139,87,0.25); border-radius:20px; padding:30px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:72px; font-weight:900; color:#2E8B57; line-height:1;\">99%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top:10px; line-height:1.4;\">of phones in India<br>now made domestically</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Big stat: 85% -->\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(184,115,51,0.15) 0%, rgba(184,115,51,0.05) 100%); border:1px solid rgba(184,115,51,0.25); border-radius:20px; padding:30px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:72px; font-weight:900; color:#B87333; line-height:1;\">85%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top:10px; line-height:1.4;\">reduction in<br>mobile phone imports</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Data Cards Row 2 -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:770px; left:40px; right:40px; display:flex; gap:20px;\">\n\n    <!-- 200% jobs -->\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(232,160,76,0.15) 0%, rgba(232,160,76,0.05) 100%); border:1px solid rgba(232,160,76,0.25); border-radius:20px; padding:30px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:72px; font-weight:900; color:#E8A04C; line-height:1;\">200%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top:10px; line-height:1.4;\">increase in manufacturing<br>jobs (2022 to 2024)</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- $300B target -->\n    <div style=\"flex:1; background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 100%); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); border-radius:20px; padding:30px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:72px; font-weight:900; color:#FFFFFF; line-height:1;\">$300B</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:15px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin-top:10px; line-height:1.4;\">electronics production<br>target by 2026</div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Progress bar visual -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:990px; left:40px; right:40px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom:10px;\">India's Electronics Manufacturing Journey</div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0;\">\n      <!-- 2014 -->\n      <div style=\"text-align:center; width:120px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-weight:600;\">2014</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:11px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\">Make in India<br>launched</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; height:8px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(184,115,51,0.3), #B87333); border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <!-- 2020 -->\n      <div style=\"text-align:center; width:120px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-weight:600;\">2020</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:11px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\">Atmanirbhar<br>Bharat</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"flex:1; height:8px; background:linear-gradient(90deg, #B87333, #2E8B57); border-radius:4px;\"></div>\n      <!-- 2026 -->\n      <div style=\"text-align:center; width:120px;\">\n        <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:#2E8B57; font-weight:700;\">2026</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size:11px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);\">$300B Target<br>&#127919;</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Bottom callout -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:80px; left:40px; right:40px; background:rgba(184,115,51,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(184,115,51,0.15); border-radius:16px; padding:20px 28px; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:36px;\">&#127470;&#127475;</div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#FFFFFF;\">LG &amp; Samsung announced major R&amp;D expansions in India (Oct 2025)</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:13px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Focusing on semiconductor design, SoC, and AI technologies</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:24px; left:40px; right:40px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-weight:600;\">cucircuits.com</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Sources: PIB India, IBEF, Business Standard</div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
